metadata.name: foggy twins
metadata.description:
One morning I checked my weather app and it told me that it was a foggy morning. A quick glance out of the window confirmed this.
It's kind of a disease but when I see fog I automaticly grab my camera and hit the streets.
On this special day I took my flying camera for a walk and together we discovered what's happening above these clouds. And now I can tell you it's magic!

The Cologne Cathedral was built in 1248 but no one else has ever shot a picture like this!
The uniqueness is the reason I offer it to the NFT community
